 Description: 
Dantes Inferno, transport players to the Other Side recreated by the Italian poet Dante Alighieri in the S. XIII in the first part of the classic, "The Divine Comedy. 
Dantes Inferno tells the story of Alighieri and his representation of hell in this action game in 3rd person. Players will be placed on the skin of Dante, who descends into hell after finding the corpse of his beloved Beatrice. Dante will get to work to rescue Beatrice, but soon realizes that in hell will have to confront their own demons and ultimately save himself.
